#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2
msgid "Vector general"
msgstr "Bendri vektoriniai"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:15
msgid "Assign projection"
msgstr "Priskirti projekciją"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:16
msgid "Assigns a new projection to a vector layer."
msgstr "Priskiria vektoriniam sluoksniui naują projekciją."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:18
msgid ""
"It creates a new layer with the exact same features and geometries as the "
"input one, but assigned to a new CRS. The geometries are **not** "
"reprojected, they are just assigned to a different CRS."
msgstr ""
"Sukuria naują sluoksnį su lygiai tokiais pačiais geoobjektais ir "
"geometrijomis kaip ir įvesties, tik su priskirta nauja CRS. Geometrijos "
"**nėra** perprojektuojamos, joms tiesiog priskiriama kita CRS."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:22
msgid ""
"This algorithm can be used to repair layers which have been assigned an "
"incorrect projection."
msgstr ""
"Šį algoritmą galima naudoti taisant sluoksnius, kuriems buvo priskirta "
"neteisinga projekcija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:25
msgid "Attributes are not modified by this algorithm."
msgstr "Šis algoritmas nekeičia atributų."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:27
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisdefinecurrentprojection`, :ref:`qgisfindprojection`, "
":ref:`qgisreprojectlayer`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisdefinecurrentprojection`, :ref:`qgisfindprojection`, "
":ref:`qgisreprojectlayer`"

